Nohla Therapeutics is pioneering new universal donor expanded cord blood therapies to save livesOur universal donor therapies are available on demand, targeting hematopoietic recovery and chemotherapy induced neutropenia, and are being extended to treat a range of other medical indications.About our scientific platform › 








