Company Overview of Nohla Therapeutics Inc.



Snapshot People




Company Overview
Nohla Therapeutics Inc. develops and manufactures ex vivo expanded universal donor cellular therapies to treat patients with cancer and other life threatening illnesses. Its universal donor product is used to treat hematopoietic recovery, chemotherapy induced neutropenia, and other medical indications. The company was founded in 2015 and is based in Seattle, Washington.


1616 Eastlake Avenue EastSuite 202Seattle, WA 98102United StatesFounded in 2015



Phone: 206-310-5560

nohlatherapeutics.com







